cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CR 

The paper deals with image-based localisation, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of binary descriptors and CNN classifiers also suggests a focus on machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI, cs.LG). The application of the approach to urban environments and the consideration of left or right turns over a route suggest a potential application in robotics and automation (cs.RO). Finally, the use of descriptors and classifiers for matching also suggests a potential application in computer security and cryptography (cs.CR).
